erything to Nothing: The Poetry of the Great War, Revolution and the Transformation of Europe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tBDUBwAAQBAJ&pg=PT139|date=16 February 2016|publisher=Verso Books|isbn=978-1-78478-150-7|pages=139\u2013}}\n*{{cite book|author=James Lyon|title=Serbia and the Balkan Front, 1914: The Outbreak of the Great War|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vMkfCgAAQBAJ|date=30 July 2015|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|isbn=978-1-4725-8005-4}}\n*{{cite book|author=Stevan K. Pavlowitch|title=A History of the Balkans 1804-1945|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZGugBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA211|date= 2014|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-317-90017-7}}\n{{refend}}\n\n== External Links ==\n\n*{{Cite web|url=http://www.rts.rs/page/stories/ci/Velikirat/story/2525/srbi-na-krfu/2175352/od-srbije-do-krfa--put-albanske-golgote.html|title=From Serbia to Corfu, the path of the Albanian Golgotha|last=Zari\u0107|first=Sladjana|date=2016|website=www.rts.rs|language=sr|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}\n* [http://www.odbrana.mod.gov.rs/specijalni%20prilog/135/Odbrana%20246%20-%20Specijalni%20prilog%20135%20-%20Zivot%20u%20okupiranoj%20Srbiji%201915-1918..pdf Life in occupied Serbia 1915 \u2013 1918], Magazine \u2033Defense\u2033, special edition No 135, Miljan Milkich, December 15, 2015. (Serbian)\n* [http://www.odbrana.mod.gov.rs/specijalni%20prilog/136/Odbrana%20247%20-%20Specijalni%20prilog%20136%20-%20Albanska%20golgota%20Srpske%20vojske.pdf Golgotha of Serbian Army], Magazine \u2033Defense\u2033, special edition No 136, Snezana Nikolich, January 1, 2016. (Serbian)\n* [http://www.odbrana.mod.gov.rs/specijalni%20prilog/138/Odbrana-250-Spec%20prilog%20138.pdf In the bosom of Bizerte], Magazine \u2033Defense\u2033, special edition No 138, Snezana Nikolich, February 15, 2016. (Serbian)\n* [http://www.odbrana.mod.gov.rs/specijalni%20prilog/148/Specijalni%20prilog%20148.pdf Corfu \u2013 Island of Solvation], Magazine \u2033Defense\u2033, special edition No 148, Milan Milkic, July 15, 2016. (Serbian)\n \n{{DEFAULTSORT:Great Retreat (Serbian)}}\n\n{{World War I}}\n{{Wars and battles involving Serbs}}\n\n[[Category:Serbia in World War I]]\n[[Category:Conflicts in 1914]]\n[[Category:Conflicts in 1915]]\n[[Category:1914 in Serbia]]\n[[Category:1915 in Serbia]]\n[[Category:1915 in Albania]]\n[[Category:November 1914 events]]\n[[Category:Albania in World War I]]\n[[Category:Battles of World War I involving Serbia]]\n[[Category:Battles of World War I involving Austria-Hungary]]\n[[Category:Battles of World War I involving Germany]]\n[[Category:Battles of World War I involving Bulgaria]]\n[[Category:Battles of the Balkans Theatre (World War I)]]\n[[Category:Battles involving Serbia]]\n[[Category:Battles involving Austria]]\n", "name_user": "Aeengath", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Great_Retreat_(Serbian)"}
